OL,3,CEx-Derbyshire Police officer jailed
OL,4,Cfor causing death by dangerous driving
OL,6,FA former Derbyshire Police officer has
OL,7,Fbeen sentenced after admitting causing
OL,8,Fdeath by dangerous driving.
OL,10,F55-year-old Michael Cooper admitted to
OL,11,Fthe charge, as well as causing serious
OL,12,Finjury by dangerous driving after a
OL,13,Ffatal collision in Egginton Road in
OL,14,FEtwall in Derbyshire, at around noon
OL,15,Fon 28 September 2021.
OL,17,FHe was jailed for three years and
OL,18,Fseven months at Nottingham Crown Court
OL,19,Fon Friday 17 July.
