OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1784310505
OL,3,CEx-Derbyshire Police officer jailed
OL,4,Cfor causing death by dangerous driving
OL,6,FThe former Detective Chief Inspector
OL,7,Fwas charged last year after an
OL,8,Finvestigation by the Independent
OL,9,FOffice for Police Conduct (IOPC).
OL,11,FMr Cooper was a serving officer at the
OL,12,Ftime of the fatal collision, but
OL,13,Fresigned prior to the conclusion of
OL,14,Fassociated conduct matters.
OL,16,FThe court heard how he crashed his
OL,17,Funmarked police car, killing
OL,18,Feducational psychologist 50-year-old
OL,19,FJames Bane, and throwing a woman into
OL,20,Fthe air.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1784310505
OL,3,CEx-Derbyshire Police officer jailed
OL,4,Cfor causing death by dangerous driving
OL,6,FMr Cooper told officers after the
OL,7,Fcrash he had not been advised on any
OL,8,F"special thing to do" about driving
OL,9,Fand refused to give access to his
OL,10,Fmedical records.
OL,12,FBut the court heard he had been asked
OL,13,Fby a neurologist in 2009 to stop
OL,14,Fdriving and contact the Driver and
OL,15,FVehicle Licensing Agency (DVLA)
OL,16,Fbecause he had episodes of randomly
OL,17,Fcollapsing.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@UO]
