PN,34204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1784310505
OL,3,CEx-Derbyshire Police officer jailed
OL,4,Cfor causing death by dangerous driving
OL,6,FSentencing Cooper, Mr Justice Sweeting
OL,7,Ftold the defendant there was a
OL,8,F"callous disregard of potential
OL,9,Fdanger", adding: "Your guilt lies in
OL,10,Fthe decision to drive at all."
OL,12,FThe judge said: "The risk may have
OL,13,Fbeen intermittent and unpredictable,
OL,14,Fbut it was a risk you knew existed."
OL,16,FIn a statement read to the court, Mr
OL,17,FBane's wife, Katherine Bane, said: "He
OL,18,Fwas a thoughtful, dedicated, respected
OL,19,Fand greatly missed educational
OL,20,Fpsychologist.
OL,26,@pD@AOUqD@GO]qD@ROUrD@^O]tD@QOUvD@dO]yD@
OL,26,AdOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
