PN,34206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1784310505
OL,3,CEx-Derbyshire Police officer jailed
OL,4,Cfor causing death by dangerous driving
OL,6,FDefence barrister Adrian Keeling KC
OL,7,Fread aloud a letter written by Cooper,
OL,8,Fwhich said: "I can't begin to imagine
OL,9,Fthe unbearable pain and grief
OL,10,Ffollowing the death of Mr Bane in
OL,11,Fparticular. I'm deeply sorry."
OL,13,FCooper will have to take an extended
OL,14,Fretest if he is deemed medically fit
OL,15,Fto drive in the future, the court
OL,16,Fheard.
OL,26,@pD@MOUsD@^O]
